      "writtenOn": "2010-10-14T16:54:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The idea is that you might want to have different instances (probably of the same AVD) boot up using different technologies, which I assume wouldn\u0027t be possible when placing the configuration file in the AVD content directory. Any other way to doing this?. Also, this file should ideally be maintenance free, but can be tweaked by the user.",
